HEADWORD: Trant
<hw>Trant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[Cf. OD.
<ets>tranten</ets> to walk slowly, LG. & D. <ets>trant</ets> walk,
pace.]</ety> <def>To traffic in an itinerary manner; to peddle.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>traunt</asp>.]</altsp> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
